&lt;li&gt;Help ensure Discord’s data processing globally complies with all applicable privacy laws, including the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and state and federal consumer protection and privacy laws&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as one of the company’s experts on issues related to privacy, ML development, and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with colleagues in Legal on privacy issues that arise in the development of new products and technologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead internal projects, process development, and training to empower the business and your colleagues&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
